<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued December 25 at 1:00PM EST until December 25 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Boston</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST THIS
EVENING...
* WHAT...Freezing rain. Ice accumulations of a light glaze to less
than one tenth of an inch.
* WHERE...Portions of northern Connecticut and central and
western Massachusetts.
* WHEN...Until 7 PM EST this evening.
* IMPACTS...Slippery travel conditions, especially on untreated
surfaces.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.</instruction>
